Package edu.up.cs301.game.infoMsg

Class Summary
BindGameInfo A message from the game to a player that tells the player: - who the game is - what the player's ID number is (i.e., player 0, player 1, etc.)
GameInfo An informational message that is sent from the game to a player.
GameOverInfo A message from the game to a player that tells the player that the game is over.
GameState The state of the game.
IllegalMoveInfo The a message from the game to a player that the move just attempted was illegal.
NotYourTurnInfo The a message from the game to a player that the move just attempted was made at a time when they were not allowed to move.
StartGameInfo The a message from the game to a player that game is ready to start.
TimerInfo The a message from to a player (typically sent by a timer) that the timer's clock has "ticked".
